PublicRemarks: Plan E, the South-East facing two bedroom + two bathroom corner home offers a generously proportioned covered balcony for year-round outdoor dining and entertaining. Full-size 30' integrated Fisher & Paykel / Bosch appliance package with 5-burner gas cooktop and brilliant storage solutions are included. Along with, over-height doors, 9' ceilings, wide-plank European flooring, A/C and built-in wardrobe systems. Enjoy the convenience of extensive building amenities, one block from Burquitlam Skytrain, minutes from SFU, parks, trails, shopping, restaurants and more! Contact sales manager. (29311531)

PublicRemarks: QUEENS PARK~ This hidden gem 3 level townhouse like a DETACHED with a 14 unit complex is nestled in the heritage houses of Park Row. Bring your decoration ideas & style, a lot of potential.. More than 2100 + sq of family-friendly living space , 3 bed+ den and flex room or 4th Bed and 2 1/2 baths, steps from New Westminster's best Queen's park. The main level boasts an open concept living/dining rm with cozy gas fireplace and a lovely eat in kitchen. Off the living rm is a spacious private outdoor patio surrounded by mature landscape, perfect for entertaining. Upstairs, 3brms, including primary w/ensuite and balcony and full bath, downstairs huge rec room for kids, storage and an office or den. Pet friendly, Family friendly, proactive strata & just a 10 min walk to Skytrain. OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY FEB 18, 2-4P.M (29288335)

PublicRemarks: Townhome with ELEVATOR SERVICE to all 3 floors!! Thinking of retiring in a multi-level townhome but don't like climbing the stairs? Look no further!! This 3 level END UNIT town home comes with its own private elevator to access all 3 floors. Extra large tandem garage with extra wide garage door. Lots of storage space. No need to retire in a condo. Consider this quality built townhome development by DAVA. All Hardie Plank exterior with glass panel balcony & large patio. 9' ceiling on main floor, open kitchen design with premium stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, easy-care vinyl planking on main floor. Convenient location with short stroll to the Transit Station & a 5 min drive to Walmart super centre and Queensborough Shopping Centre. (28795196)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to 7433 Magnolia Terrace, a Bright & Spotless RARE END UNIT townhouse in Burnaby´s Highgate neighbourhood. 3 Levels, 3 Bdrms, 2 Baths. As you walk in, you´re met with a large LR with a cozy gas fireplace and a large Kitchen + dining area. Above the main is 2 good sized bedrooms, full-sized laundry, and a cheater ensuite. PublicRemarks: Tastefully renovated 3 bedroom townhouse in Simon Fraser Hills! PublicRemarks: Welcome to Perla by Polygon, where you will enjoy park tranquility and Metrotown urban energy at the same time. Steps away, Central Park offers year-round beauty and lively spaces for fun events. An inexhaustible assortment of brand-name stores, dining and entertainment options are also available just down a tree-lined boulevard. This thoughtfully laid out floorplan features 9' ceilings, air-conditioned interiors, and a sleek kitchen appointed with Fulgar Milano appliances, and a large ensuite with dual sinks and a spa shower. Just an elevator ride away, over 20,000 sq. ft. of residents-only amenities offer a luxurious work-life balance. (29239267)

PublicRemarks: Rarely available ''Thurston Street" located in a quite cul-de-sac in West Burnaby. Upper corner unit with BIG windows. Bright north facing 2 bedrooms plus 1.5 baths. Functional layout and full of details. Spacious living and dining rooms. Open concept kitchen with large Island with plenty of cabinet spaces, quartz composite counter-tops, SS appliances, newer front load W/D. Laminate flooring throughout the main floor, powder room on main. This home with a big size of balcony. Just steps to schools, Central Park, skytrain station, shopping and minutes to Metrotown, Crystal Mall, Community Centre, BCIT. TWO side by side parking spots plus a storage locker. Easy to show. Open House FEB. 17 SAT 2-4 pm. (29223326)

PublicRemarks: Corner 2 bedroom + den at Bordeaux built by award winning developer, Solterra. This home spans the entire NW side of the community. Features 227sf of outdoor space with panoramic view facing Northwest, showcasing Brentwood, mountains, and DT Vancouver. Floor to ceiling windows throughout the home to maximize natural light with central AC/Heating. 2 spa-inspired bathrooms with heated floors in the Primary ensuite. Stunning imported kitchen cabinetry from Italy with appliances including Liebherr & Fulgor Milano brands. 1 parking stall and storage locker included. (29262626)

PublicRemarks: Smith & Farrow by Boffo superior design, unparalleled craftsmanship. Enjoy unobstructed north-west mountain views right from the window at your kitchen sink. The bright kitchen overlooks a generous 233sqft balcony equipped with gas outlet and exterior lighting. Full-size 30" integrated Fisher & Paykel / Bosch appliance package with 5-burner gas cooktop and an abundance of storage including pantry wall. Choose your favourite custom kitchen table design at dining or counter height, made with cabinetry material and stone countertops. Ensuite features heated flooring, cabinetry drawers, medicine cabinets and multi-paneled mirrors with integrated lighting. 9' ceilings, European wide-plank flooring, air conditioning, three floors of amenities including outdoor pool and more! (29312091)

PublicRemarks: Indulge in breathtaking panoramic views of the mountains & skyline frm this captivating 2beds, 2baths corner unit! Crafted by Polygon, this exceptional condo is strategically positioned just a block away frm the Patterson Skytrain Station, ensuring seamless connectivity. Adorned w high-end appliances, air conditioning, & floor-to-ceiling windows that flood the interiors w natural light. The generous living & dining areas, coupled w a master bedroom featuring an ensuite & walk-in closet. Extend your living space to a spacious balcony, perfect for hosting friends & family against the stunning backdrop. Embrace an active lifestyle with Central Park at your doorstep, offering the ideal setting for morning jogs or evening runs. The lobby exudes modernity and trendiness, provides comfortable seating as you await friends or the convenience of Uber Eats. Steps to Metrotown, Bby Library, Crystal Mall & Kingsway shops & restaurants. Chaffey-Burke Elementary & Moscrop Sec. OH, Sat & Sun, Feb 17 & 18, 3.30pm - 5.30pm. (29374195)

PublicRemarks: Cirrus at Solo District in Brentwood. Steps to Whole foods, new Brentwood Mall and skytrain station, restaurants, stores and etc. Oversized kitchen with stainless steel Bosch professional lines appliances, quartz counter-tops, pantry cabinet and tons of storage space. PublicRemarks: Stop looking, your home is here! This luxurious 2 bed+den, 2.5 bath townhouse boasts a spacious private patio, meticulously maintained and perfect for a lifestyle of quality and taste. No details spared, featuring integrated European appliances with a 5-burner gas cooktop, AC, polished Quartz stone countertops in both the kitchen and the spa-inspired bathrooms, and soft-close cabinetry. Skytrain station and Bonsor Recreation Centre are all within walking distance, offering a blend of urban convenience and tranquility. Amazing amenities include a fitness center, yoga room, hotel-like guest suite, bike storage, and attentive concierge services. Includes 2 parkings and 1 locker (29345853)

Property.Address.AddressText: 8 1211 EWEN AVENUE|New Westminster, British Columbia V3M5E5

PublicRemarks: Welcome to this stunning 3-year new 3 level townhouse in central location of New West. This home features 1452 sqft, 4 bedrooms & 2.5 bathrooms w/attached single garage with extra storage space and private fenced yard. Main floor boasts an open concept Floorplan with a bright living room and gourmet kitchen with S/S appliances, quartz countertop, pantry and an island. Downstair's bedroom provides a flexible use for bedroom or home office. 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths on the top floor. The built-in security system and remaining of 2/5/10 Warranty offer peace of mind. Shop the River Market or walk the waterfront by the Quay. Easy access to the skytrain. Nearby Moody Park features a pool. Lord Kelvin Elementary and New West Secondary catchment and Douglas College nearby. OH Feb. 17 & 18 2-4pm. (29359589)

Property.Address.AddressText: 3 1023 THIRD AVENUE|New Westminster, British Columbia V3M1P6

PublicRemarks: Live at the top of New Westminster! Stunning Penthouse featuring 270 degree views of the city, mountains, and the Fraser River. This 2 Bedroom + Den & 2 Bathroom Condo features 1,408 Sq Ft of living space and an extremely functional layout maximizing your space. Entry way foyer, second bedroom with sliding door to the balcony, private den, Master Bedroom with double closets and ensuite 5 piece bathroom with soaker tub and shower, and open concept kitchen overlooking the living room with gas fireplace. Expansive windows in the living room providing ample amounts of light and vantage point of the stunning views. Massive 284 Sq Ft outdoor patio perfect for entertaining. Central AC and concrete building. 2 parking, 1 locker, and amenities on the 9th floor. Skytrain next door & rentals allowed! (29340319)

PublicRemarks: Newly built CONCRETE 3 bed/3 bath townhouse in the heart of downtown located in between 2 skytrain stations.  Ideal for families and downsizers, this 2-level home has an open living/dining room, bedroom and kitchen on the main floor with high-end Bosch appliances including 5 burner gas cooktop. Upstairs has 2 bedrooms featuring overheight 15 ft ceilings with gigantic windows and XL primary room with it's own private balcony! Private outdoor patio for summer BBQ. Bonus 2 side-by-side parking stalls plus external locker. Air-conditioned.  Amenities include guest suite, 30,000 sf outdoor garden space, fitness gym, outdoor children's play area, lounge with kitchen, community garden.  Steps to everything including the Quay, restaurants, cafes, shops and more! (29286331)

PublicRemarks: Cascade Village Townhouse: Just under 2000 square ft on 2 levels, this house-size townhome is a quiet end unit with 619 sqft of private & fully fenced outdoor patio/deck space.  Main floor features large living rm w/fireplace & high ceilings, dining rm, family rm off kitchen, a powder rm, and a large laundry/utility rm.  Upper level has 2 super-size & spacious bdrms & 2 bthrms.  Comes w/2 parking spaces: 1 in the semi-private garage & another in the secure underground parkade.  Amenities include pool, hot tub, sauna, gym, theatre rm, clubhouse, & guest suite.  A solid & well-maintained complex in a park like setting.  Centrally located & walking distance to Burnaby Hospital, schools, and restaurants.  A must see! (29261795)

PublicRemarks: Impeccably updated duplex-style 4 bed+den 3 bath townhome nestled in serene, park-like setting at Willowleaf Place in Burnaby North. This spacious home boasts extensive updated inside and out, including a new roof (2012), windows (2015), and siding replacement (2023). Luxurious interior features include a gourmet kitchen with SS fridge and range (2021), heated floors, renovated bathrooms with ceiling skylight, and high-end finishes throughout. Enjoy energy efficiency with newer gas furnace, hot water tank, insulation, and LED lighting. Step out to relax on the large rear deck with a custom artisan-crafted concrete Natural Gas "Dreamworks" fire table and privacy with 10' laurel privacy hedge. Short 10 mins drive to Lougheed Mall or easy access to No.1 Highway (29339719)

PublicRemarks: Live at REDBRICK HEIGHTS, the most coveted townhome development in the popular BURNABY HEIGHTS community! This stylish 3 bedroom home is freshly painted & features a great open floorplan, spacious rooms & sundeck on each floor offering some stunning city views. School Catchment: Gilmore & Alpha. OPEN HOUSE Sat Feb 10, 2-4pm & Sun Feb 11, 1-3pm (29329590)

PublicRemarks: Concrete townhome with direct street access and a huge patio all within this vibrant community in the heart of Burnaby. PublicRemarks: Welcome to newly build "Alto on Capitol Hill by Vivid Green Architecture in Burnaby North. This beautifully made 2 Bedroom 2 Bath Plus Study Den condo constructed, made right on Hastings Street and Ellesmere Avenue. You have den as a bonus which could be used as extra bedroom or as an workspace. This Development includes a 4 storey wood- frame low-rise above 2 levels of parking, offering 20 luxury condos, 11 live-work units and 5 commercial retail units. PublicRemarks: Welcome to Modello by Boffo, perfectly located in the heart of Metrotown. This spacious open concept 2 bedroom 2 bathroom condo offers a chef's kitchen equipped with fully integrated Miele appliances, a large island, quartz countertops, ample storage, and wine fridge. With 9-foot ceilings, geothermal heating and cooling, and a covered patio, this unit is the epitome of luxury comfort. The primary bedroom is generously sized and can easily accommodate king-sized furnishings, while the spa-inspired ensuite boasts marble heated floors, a double vanity, and a luxurious soaking tub. Modello residents enjoy unrivaled amenities including a 24-hour concierge, indoor and outdoor lounges, a state-of-the-art gym, sauna, and jacuzzi. With convenient access to the sky train, shops, restaurants, and more, this is Metrotown living at its finest. One parking spot and storage included. Schedule your viewing today! Open Sat Feb 17th 12:30 - 2:00 (29355025)

PublicRemarks: RARE OPPORTUNITY! Indulge in resort living at the top of world in this exquisite SUB-PENTHOUSE swooning over the breathtaking panoramic views in every room from Mt Baker to Vancouver Island. PublicRemarks: Feels like a House - wide and shallow Unique floor plan offers exceptional versatility! Lower level offers a south facing 313 Sq Ft  Patio, Full Bath, Bedroom, Den, Mudroom, plus 125 square ft Private Storage Room & secure Tandem Garage! Main Level features a  Wall of Windows, Open Kitchen, Living & Dining Room, Family Room (or 4th bed) & 259 Sq Ft Patio! Up is 2 Beds, 2 Full Baths, plus Fraser River Views from the Balcony! Amenities include a well equipped Gym, Party Room and Outdoor Pool! LOCATION: 3 bus stops nearby, 10 min to Skytrain, walk to the new Rec Center and Pool (2024), Queens Park across the street! Close to Shopping, Restaurants, Sapperton, Korea Town, and City of Lougheed! This is a Special home that offers space and storage (additional locker) for both downsizers or a growing family. Perhaps the perfect size to call home for years to come! (29241604)

PublicRemarks: Starling at Lumina in the heart of Brentwood. Bright townhome features with open concept floor plan, laminate flooring through-out, 9 ft´ ceilings, A/C and floor to ceiling windows. Kitchen boasts modern, full size integrated S/S Bosch appliances, gas cooktop, hoodfan, quartz countertops, soft close cabinetry and a large island perfect for entertaining. Spacious masterbedroom hosts a walk-through closet into the spa-inspired ensuite. Amenities include, Fitness Centre, Yoga Rooms, Social Lounges & BBQ area, Guest Suites & 24/7 hr Concierge. Just steps away from Brentwood Town Center & Skytrain. Bonus 2 Parkings & 1 Storage. Openhouse SAT Sept 9 2-4PM, SUN Sept 10 3-5PM. (28760722)

PublicRemarks: What if you COULD have it all? Single level Sky Suite living in the heart of Lougheed on the 44th floor. This brand new 3 bedroom home is perfect if you're looking to downsize, or grow the family. Three spacious bedrooms with plenty of storage space. The master features a huge walk in closet. Two balconies offer amazing views, and the principal one has the added luxury of a patio below, so you don't feel like you're that high up in the building. Double fridge freezer, house size side by side laundry with plenty of additional space solves all the typical condo living issues. Parking and storage. Building amenities are unsurpassed, featuring a huge gym, party rooms, outdoor kitchens, pitch & putt - more like a country club! Walk to the mall & SkyTrain. Call today for your private showing. (29366928)

PublicRemarks: Charming Craftsman Home w/veranda overlooking a wonderful landscaped front garden & water feature! Spacious & open layout. Tranquil location just steps to enjoy sunny walks along the beach.  Open house Saturday, August 12, 2023, 2pm to 4pm. (28651500)

PublicRemarks: Attention downsizers! Beautiful 3-brm + flex CORNER home with 9-ft ceilings. A/C and open plan with bright SW exposure. PublicRemarks: BREATHTAKING Bright + airy 2-brm + flex CORNER suite with covered balcony at Smith & Farrow by Boffo. Quiet residential street one block from Burquitlam Skytrain and 5-minutes from SFU. (29312104)

PublicRemarks: This lovingly maintained spacious 1911 square ft 1/2 duplex is the perfect home for the growing family. Situated across from the large Robert Burnaby Park, it provides a serene environment filled with greenery. The upstairs contains 3 bedrooms, with an open living room/dining room/kitchen that leads to the large back yard makes this an optimal setting for parties large or small. Recent upgrades include a new water tank, recently replaced furnace and windows, and various other updates. The lower floor contains a secondary suite that can be rented as a 2 bedroom suite, the ideal mortgage helper. Just minutes away from Highway 1, Edmonds CC, and Deer Lake. School Catchments: Lakeview Elementary and Burnaby Central Secondary. (29003731)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Akimbo by Imani Development - an architectural masterpiece proudly designed by award-winning IBI Group Architects. This NW corner 3 -bed 2-bath + den home features 1,175 sqft living space & gorgeous 260 sqft wrap-around balcony overlooking city and mountain views. Akimbo offers generous, luxurious sense of space with over-height 9' ceilings, floor-to-ceiling windows, state-of-the-art kitchen, spa-like bathrooms, individually controlled air conditioning & heating for year-round climate control throughout the home. Centrally located in Brentwood, conveniently close to shopping mall, restaurants, groceries, transit & highways. GST is not included in the purchase price. 2 parking stall & 1 locker included. Showing by appointment only (29258118)

PublicRemarks: Great opportunity to own a Live/Work unit featuring 648 square ft above plus 600 square ft on the main level. Upper floor offers a 2-bdrm, 2-bath, full kitchen, self-contained residential space w/balcony. Main floor offers Commercial/office unit CD-zoned with 12-14' height ceilings plus full 4-pc accessible washroom, can be used as 3rd bedroom or rented if needed. So you can have your own space and still have rental income. Lots of building amenities include courtyard, gym, guest suite, games & meeting rooms, golf simulator, party lounge, outdoor BBQ, dining terrace & 24-hr concierge. Included one (1) Parking $40,000 benefit and (1) locker. (29103520)

PublicRemarks: Experience opulent living at Modello quality built by Boffo, centrally located in Metrotown. PublicRemarks: Welcome to this exquisite townhouse with upgraded features on every floor. Security is ensured with a modern system. Enjoy infloor heating, new appliances, and hardwood throughout. The kitchen boasts Fisher & Paykel appliances and Bosch dishwasher. The main level features LED lights, shutters, and two fireplaces. Upstairs offers 3 bedrooms and renovated bathrooms. PublicRemarks: Welcome to this beautiful family home. 4 bedrooms up and 1 bed walk out suite with a covered deck. Currently seller has rented it as 7 beds up and 1 bed down. Upstairs, It has a spacious kitchen with a view of the city and mountains and leads to a huge sundeck with the same view! Very bright with skylights and high ceilings. Lots of storage space all over the house as well as a crawl space. Close to public transit , shopping, parks and schools. A Must SEE! (29078380)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Southpointe, three-level townhouse built by Polygon. This beautiful townhouse is the perfect oasis for your family to reside. The main floor  featuring a private garden entrance which leads to the 9ft ceiling, spacious living and dining room, open kitchen concept with newly updated cabinets, new modern laminate floors, light fixtures and fresh paint throughout. Large south-facing sundeck for your family to enjoy this outdoor space, attached side-by-side double garage, the list goes on. Convenient location close to Edmond Sky train Station, steps away from Taylor Park, Byrne Creek Park and urban hiking trails. This townhouse offers great living in the heart of this popular & safe neighbourhood. Call and book your private showings. (29005303)

PublicRemarks: Live next to a Future 2.5 acre park in a spacious home by award-winning developer, Beedie Living. Featuring a large rooftop patio with gas & water bibs, a balcony & direct access to the community courtyard, there is plenty of private outdoor space. Abundant storage with a side-by-side washer & dryer with shelving, a pantry, and a storage locker. A beautiful modern kitchen includes integrated appliances and a gas cooktop. Retreat to your master ensuite with heated floors and double vanity. Walk to schools, shops and restaurants. Amenities include a fitness centre, indoor/outdoor party lounge and a playground. (29293327)

Please do not walk on the property without an appointment. (29266973)

PublicRemarks: RARE 2100SF 2 Level PENTHOUSE in the Heart of Metrotown! 2 bedroom(can turn into 3 bedroom)+ Den+3 bath boasts an amazing&tranquil outlook over the Mountains,Parks,lake&City.Enjoy Unobstructed 270 degree Gorgeous Mountain/city Views. Amenities include indoor pool, hot tub, sauna&Steam, squash courts, indoor basketball, gym, rec-room. Steps to Metrotown Shopping Mall, Burnaby Public Library,Community Center, Skytrain Station, Deer Lake Park, T&T, Crystal Mall, Restaurants. 2parking stalls+1 storage locker. You can never a 2 level home this size in Metrotown, don't miss out this fabulous suite!!! Open house June 17 SAT 2-4PM (28390058)

PublicRemarks: ÉTOILE- Redefining Modern Luxury. Exclusive 3 level Townhouse with spacious, open, modern interior designed for entertaining & easy living by Chil Interior Design. Beautiful 3 bdrm, 4 bath. RARE to find separate floor of live/work space with private entrance on street level. Live/work space is ideal for commercial/studio use with it's own fridge, cabinets, sink and microwave. Comes with quartz countertops, high performance stainless steel appliances and 2 parking stalls! Étoile's rooftop oasis has an outdoor pool, hot tub, sundeck with cabana, green space & playground. Each tower has its own private social lounge & fitness centre complete with his & her steam rooms. Just Minutes from Brentwood Town Centre, dining & entertainment. Walking distance to skytrain. OPEN HOUSE MAY 20-21 12:30-1:30 (28385341)

PublicRemarks: An extraordinary opportunity beckons to make this exceptional 5-level, air-conditioned concrete townhouse your very own in the stunning Triomph Tower. This spacious 4-bedroom townhome boasts top-of-the-line Bosch stainless steel appliances, elegant quartz countertops, lofty 9-foot ceilings, and a centralized air conditioning system. (29241362)

PublicRemarks: PRIME North Burnaby location. This 2 level 1/2 duplex offers an incredible opportunity to move into one of the most desired neighbourhoods in the area. With 4 Bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2,070 SqFt of living space, this makes a great family home. Upstairs features original hardwood floors, with ample entertainment space and access to a huge 395 SqFt sundeck with beautiful mountain views. Downstairs has a variety of options with separate access - Keep as part of the main home, or rent out as a 1 or 2 bedroom suite. Roof and Furnace replaced within last 5 years. School catchment area incl highly desired Westridge/Armstrong & Burnaby North/Alpha Secondary. Close to transit and an abundance of great restaurants, shopping, coffee, parks, golf and more. Showings by appointment only. (29354939)

PublicRemarks: Indulge in unparalleled panoramic views stretching from the North Shore Mountains to Vancouver's iconic skyline and beyond to Vancouver Island in this distinctive Capitol Hill home. Rebulit in the 1980s, this unique 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence exudes contemporary charm throughout. The main level welcomes with an updated modern kitchen, adjoining dining area leading to a view deck, a full bath, and two bedrooms. Upstairs, discover an airy open living room boasting a magnificent deck, perfect for all seasons. The lower level offers two more bedrooms, an office, a full bath, and a summer kitchen. With a detached single garage, ample front parking, a delightful private patio, and a low maintenance yard, this property epitomizes both convenience and serenity.OPEN HOUSE ON FEB.24& 25 2PM-4PM (29371208)

PublicRemarks: Live next to a Future 2.5 acre park in a spacious home by award-winning developer, Beedie Living. Featuring a large rooftop patio with gas & water bibs, a balcony & direct access to the community courtyard, there is plenty of private outdoor space. (29335892)

PublicRemarks: Aragon presents Timber House, the final phase of our master-planned community of Port Royal! Looking for more space for your family? PublicRemarks: Welcome to this brand new subpenhouse 3Bed&3Bath home at Hillside West by Concord Pacific in sought after Brentwood. Luxurious 48th-floor residence in prime location! PublicRemarks: A charming two-story CHARACTER home with a basement with 9 bedrooms, 5 bathrooms, and an ample activity room. This lovely property was renovated in 2020 and now features a new roof, hot water tank, windows, furnace, and kitchen. The house has a spacious living room and an open-concept dining area that seamlessly connect to a fantastic, sizeable kitchen. The house additionally includes bamboo floors, a fireplace, a patio, and a terrace. There is a lovely huge open leisure space in the basement. This house is completely fenced and has plenty of foliage for shade. The front yard blends in flawlessly and offers stunning views of the Fraser River Docks. Situated close to buses, Scott Road station, schools, and stores, and close to traffic routes. (29213718)

PublicRemarks: Step into this exquisitely renovated, ready-to-move-into family home, perfectly situated in the sought-after area between Metrotown and Brentwood. This two-story residence boasts 4 well-appointed bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and features a spacious, south-facing deck, along with a detached garage for one car plus a side parking. The interior has been repainted, complemented by newer flooring, updated bathrooms, and a laundry set. Located within the catchment areas for Cascade Heights Elementary and Moscrop Secondary, and just a short walk to both, this home is perfect for a growing family. Don't miss the opportunity to view this gem during the Open House on February 17 & 18, Saturday and Sunday from 2-4PM. (29356769)

PublicRemarks: Court order Sale. Sell as where it is.  Well-located property located along the growing Sixth Street Corridor of Burnaby. Sixth Street Area Plans supports mixed-used development at this location up to 6 storeys in form with retail at grade. This growing neighborhood has been multiple successful multifamily developments in recent years with more local businesses setting up shop, in the process of creating a vibrant community. For owner-users, the current C-4 zoning already permits usages such as automobile showroom including motor vehicle repairs & inspections retail sales of auto parts, grocery stores, a list of personal services, & many others. Great opportunity for owner-users, investors for future assembly, and developers. (29150687)

PublicRemarks: Why buy townhouse? or duplex when you can buy this non-strata single-family home in the prime south Burnaby asking only $1,688,000. Similar in price to a newer townhouse however this is a single detached home with no shared wall. 4 bedrooms, 3 1/2 washrooms, and a huge rec room waiting for your ideas. Located in desirable South Slope, 2 blocks from Clinton Elementary, minutes walk to Burnaby South Secondary, Skytrain, Parks, Metrotown, Highgate and Market Crossing malls. Stylish cabinets, quartz countertops, radiant heat, hot water on demand, EV Charging, air conditioning, HRV, security system/intercom, rope lights, and more. Truly an affordable option to own your own detached home in Burnaby, one of only a handful of similar homes ever built in Burnaby. Call for your private showing (29129494)

This home offers 2 SEPARATE SUITES: UP:3 BED+1 renovated BATH, featuring gorgeous H/W flooring upstairs, a bright southern exposure kitchen with S/S appliance. Below, there is an independent 2 bedroom + 1 bathroom basement suite with separate entrance, ideal for a Nanny's suite or for accommodating extended family members.  Situated in a great family oriented neighbourhood, conveniently close to excellent elementary & high schools, SFU and close to Sperling Skytrain Stn, Lougheed Hwy & Hwy 1. GREAT LANEWAY & DUPLEX POTENTIAL. GREAT HOLDING PROPERTY!  Asking price is less than the $1,843,700 BC ASSESSMENT. (29356389)

PublicRemarks: INVESTOR ALERT!  This 5 Bedroom 2 Bathroom Rancher Style Home with a Basement features a 2 bedroom suite in the basement with its own entry. The house sits on an almost 7000sq ft lot and includes newer stainless steel appliances in the upper suite, hardwood flooring in the main living spaces, a large sundeck for outdoor entertaining and a large well treed fenced yard. The home is centrally located off McBride Street, a few minutes away from Queens Park, the Pattullo Bridge for access to Surrey, Canada Way for access to Burnaby and within walking distance to both Ecole Glenbrook Middle School & New Westminster Secondary School & the Safeway on McBride & 8th Ave. Property has potential for laneway building (29170994)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Tower THREE at The City of Lougheed - a remarkable opportunity you won't want to miss! For the 1st time in Metro Vancouver, SHAPE is releasing a fully completed tower of 262 move-in-ready homes with air conditioning for sale. Residents will enjoy the unparalleled convenience and lifestyle of living above PriceSmart Foods, endless dining options, an evolving shopping centre and 3 skytrain lines. Neighbourhood 1 offers over 22,000sqft of Amenities including a luxurious sky garden, putting green, fitness centre, dog wash station, guest suites and more. Tower 3 is the final opportunity to own in Neighbourhood One's best location, in the coveted southeast corner. book your viewing today or call a sales associate for more info on pricing and availability. PublicRemarks: Wonderful family home located in convenient Highgate neighbourhood. Walk or drive to Edmonds Community Centre, Shopping, School, Restaurants, Transit & close to Buy Low Foods, Highgate Village Shopping including Save-On-Foods, Signature BC Liquor Store, Club 16, Starbucks, Public Library and so much more. This home features Hardwood Floors with inlay, large living room, spacious kitchen and dining space, 2 bedrooms & 4 piece bath. Down has large rec room, office & storage. Unfinished space awaits your ideas. Newer Laundry appliances in unfinished space & roughed in additional bathroom. Many updates include: Vinyl windows, new 2 car garage, Perimeter drainage, Ductless air conditioning, Furnace, roof, hot water tank, new deck w/aluminum railing, brand new vinyl planking in bathroom & more. PublicRemarks: SOLO 3, THE MOST DESIRABLE COMMUNITY IN BRENTWOOD. Proudly built by Apia Development. PublicRemarks: Welcome to this meticulously maintained rancher with a fully finished basement in the Garden Village area in South Burnaby! PublicRemarks: 145 E Seventh Ave is nestled perfectly in this quiet neighbourhood. This tastefully updated home is perfect for any growing family with enough space for everyone. PublicRemarks: Don't miss this prime AAA office Lease/Sale Opportunity in Metrotown. This 6th-floor corner unit offers peaceful surroundings with no obstructions, benefiting from south and east-facing windows for ample natural light. On-site retail, concierge services, and fiber-optic technology for high-speed connectivity are available. Plus, you're just steps away from the SkyTrain. Elevate your business in the heart of Metrotown! (34313388)

PublicRemarks: Opportunity to purchase a 13,068 sq.ft. (0.3 acre) riverfront property in Queensborough, New Westminster. Zoned RQ-1 with a maximum FSR of 0.5, uses such as docks, marine commercial, and wharfs are permitted under the "intertidal" designation, as long as the surrounding natural habitat is enhanced. The property has approximately 595 linear feet of riverfront along the Annacis Cannel, is fenced along South Dyke Road with two gated access points, and there are three buildings on site ' a 960 sq.ft. shed, an 1,800 sq.ft. shop, and a 640 sq.ft. warehouse. Additionally, there is a piled, hard dock fronting the property totaling approximately 1,780 sq.ft. The dock, as well as approximately 14 barge piles, are leasehold improvements which rest upon the adjacent water lot, owned by Port Metro Vancouver. The water lot is approximately 2.2 acres, and extends approximately 180 feet into the river from the lot line. A new owner with a marine use will want to renew the water lot lease. (33786256)

PublicRemarks: Very well maintained home close to amenities.  Great lot for a laneway home (buyer to verify with city). PublicRemarks: This home's diamond in the rough ready for your next investment. Situated in the Burnaby's Metrotown area, it's located in the Royal Oak Community Plan & designated to be redeveloped when assembled. The home on a 58 ft frontage lot with back lane is ready for your renovations. This home currently has 2 bedrooms on main, with a 3 piece full bathroom. In the basement with separate entrance, there are 2 bedrooms and a roughed in 3 piece bathroom. Upper level has potential for more bedrooms and bathrooms. Ample of parking available on this property for a family or multiple tenants. Upgrades were done in early 2000's for 3 phase electrical and plumbing. In the Royal Oak Plan, this M4 industrial zoned property may be assembled to create an industrial development. Call to find out more. (29169805)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to Alaska built by Amacon. This penthouse suite is where luxury and elegance meet comfort and functionality, highlighting a sleek modern design throughout. Boasting over 1,500 square feet featuring 3 bedrooms each with their own spa inspired ensuite and the addition of a powder room and den. The contemporary kitchen exhibits fully integrated appliances that flow into the main living space exemplifying an ideal open concept floorplan. PublicRemarks: Newly renovated office/showroom space primely located near the intersection of Douglas Road and Still Creek between Lougheed Highway and the Trans Canada Highway. This area is widely considered the geographic center of the Lower Mainland allowing for very quick access to all major municipalities. The Holdom Sky Train station is within walking distance. The main floor showroom area features windows on three sides for natural light, air conditioning, t-bar ceiling and pre-engineered flooring, server room, sound room, security alarm and two (2) washrooms. The second floor office features lots of windows for natural light with views of the North Shore mountains, air conditioning, t-bar ceiling and pre-engineered flooring, one (1) private office, kitchen/lunchroom, security alarm and two (2) washrooms. Five (5) parking stalls available. Please telephone or email listing agents for further information or to set up a viewing. (33914854)

Large balcony for summer BBQ overlooking the park in front of you. Main floor has another three Bdrms one full bathroom plus a huge living room and kitchen, with Separate entrance. Centrally and conveniently located near transit, Metrotown, Highgate, and Edmonds Centre.Come to show now! (29294754)

PublicRemarks: Prime location in the heart of historic Queens Park! Originally built in 1891, 5 bed, 2 bath, 2768sf home, on a large 55x148.5'lot (8166sf). Buy and renovate, sub-divide or build your dream home! Upper level: 3 bed/1 bath. Main: 1 bed/1 bath. open concept dining/living and large kitchen. Below: Laundry, 1 bed, Flex/Rec Room area. Two car detached garage. Large sunny West facing backyard. Great location, steps to Sullivan Park/Queens Park, and just blocks from Herbert Spencer Elementary and shopping on 6th. Currently tenanted. HRA Approved, potential to subdivide lot (plans available). Showings by appointment. (29335488)

PublicRemarks: Nestled within the tranquil Deer Lake Place neighborhood, this captivating home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a desirable east-facing orientation. Its prime location offers not just proximity to renowned schools, but also easy access to some of Canada's most captivating attractions, diverse shopping options, and an array of restaurants. Commuting is a breeze with convenient transit access via Hwy 1. What's particularly exciting is the forthcoming housing program by the City of Burnaby in 2024. This initiative will open doors for potential Laneway homes and multi- unit housing on single family lots, adding significant value to this property. With a spacious 7,406 square ft lot and an impressive 65 ft wide frontage, this property is poised for remarkable development opportunities. OH Sun 2-4 (29235589)

PublicRemarks: Experience modern comfort & convenience in this newly built & premium duplex nestled in the bustling Edmonds neighborhood of Burnaby. Boasting a sophisticated design, this home offers a seamless OPEN Layout w 4beds & 4baths, air conditioning, sprinkler in unit, HRV, CO2 detector & more. Main floor showcases an inviting open-concept space, featuring a spacious living area, elegant dining space, a cozy family room & a chef's dream kitchen equipped with top-tier stainless steel appliances. Additionally, a guest bedroom with an ensuite adds versatility. Upstairs, discover 3 bedrooms & a sprawling covered deck, perfect for relaxation and entertainment. Notably, this property offers the potential for a family daycare (income up to $100k/yr), complemented by the nearby Ernie Winch Park. Enjoy easy access to major highways, New Westminster, Deer Lake Park, and Surrey. Don't miss out the chance to own this high-quality duplex in one of the most sought-after neighborhood! Open House Sat & Sun, Jan 20 & 21, 2-4pm. (29197781)

PublicRemarks: 60x102 lot in prime Forest Glen neighbourhood of Central Burnaby! Stunning UNOBSTRUCTED 180 DEGREE VIEWS of North Burnaby, Capitol Hill, and the north shore mountains! PublicRemarks: Spectacular VIEWS of Downtown Vancouver and the North Shore mountains from this updated Capitol Hill home. With over 2600 square feet sprawled over three levels, this home offers the perfect family home layout. The main level features a massive primary bedroom with walk-in closet and three-piece ensuite, an open dining and living area with cozy gas fireplace and vaulted ceilings, a spacious kitchen with ample storage space and a bright eating area that leads onto a large balcony that boasts sweeping views. An additional two bedrooms and one bathroom on the upper floor with unfinished space that can easily be converted into the ultimate kid's playroom. Massive two-car garage on the lower level, along with a one-bedroom suite to help with the monthly payments. Close to bus routes, all levels of schooling, Confederation Park and all of the boutique shops and restaurants that run along Hastings Street. (29058364)

PublicRemarks: Opportunity to Acquire a Centrally Located Freestanding Building in Historic Downtown New Westminster This prime property, situated directly across from the Columbia SkyTrain station, offers exceptional accessibility and is mere minutes away from the newly renovated Pier Park. It is surrounded by a plethora of local amenities, including public spaces, retail shops, restaurants, and cafes, enriching the vibrant neighborhood. Key Features: Three Stories cof Commercial Units: The main floor features a commercial unit with an entrance on Columbia Street. The second-floor houses three units, complete with a kitchenette and washroom facilities. The lower level is occupied by a coffee-roasting cafe business facing Front Street. Unique Architectural Charm: The building showcases heritage-inspired elements, such as high ceilings and brick wall architecture, embodying the historic essence of Downtown New Westminster. Natural Light & Visibility: Large windows throughout the building ensure ample natural light. (34495806)

PublicRemarks: PRIME LOCATION IN BURNABY SOUTH! Upper Deer Lake! Semi Corner home 3beds up & 2beds down w/tremendous updates. Modern, contemporary with newly stained HARDWOOD flooring thru-out! Main kitchen is fully renovated with Caesar Stone Quartz counter tops, stainless steel appliances, stone wall tile, floor to ceiling cabinets, custom extra long drawers for double the amount of storage, 5'x7' island overlooking the open concept living room with fireplace. PublicRemarks: One of a kind custom built 3,400sqft home on a 5440sqft lot. It features 6 Bedrooms and 7 Bathrooms, with a master bedroom on the main floor. PublicRemarks: Brand new luxury 2 storey home plus basement. Main floor features a large & inviting living room w/ huge windows to enjoy the view, a dining room, spacious kitchen & spice kitchen, a family room & a powder washroom. Main floor also has a den & a bedroom with an attached washroom, potential to turn into a rental suite! 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and a laundry upstairs. The master bedroom features a walk-in closet and a spacious ensuite. Downstairs features a one-bedroom suite and a two bedroom suite **(2+1)** Basement also has a theatre & games room. This house has a potential for 3 suites, great for mortgage help! Amazing mountain, river & city views from this property. Central location with easy access to both bridges, the highway and Skytrain. (28827622)

PublicRemarks: A well built single family home situated on a QUIET street of Vancouver Heights. Top quality finishing throughout incl. OVER HEIGHT CEILINGS, Blue pearl granite in grand foyer & staircases, Solid oak wood floors, dining room & hallways, updated kitchen counter top and S/S appliances, electric stove (GAS CONNECTOR BEHIND FOR A GAS STOVE), spacious eating area & family room, HUGH COVERED DECK and in suite laundry. Upstairs with 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms with skylights and below contains a 1 bedroom suite with SEPARATE ENTRY AND ITS OWN LAUNDRY. Fully fenced backyard with detach double garage and open parking. Conveniently located to Brentwood Mall, Hastings shopping and just steps to Eileen Daily Pool and Fitness Centre. School catchments are Rosser Elementary and Alpha Secondary. (29293291)

PublicRemarks: Beautiful solid home in most prestigious Government Road Area, quiet Cul-De-Sac street. Completely refined interior modern style renovated in 2022 with all new appliances, furnace, AC and much more. It features 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths of 3 levels split. This south-facing exceptional architecturally on large 10,382 square ft lot, it provides the whole home lots of sunlight and large rear yard with absolute privacy. Lower level includes an large entertainment area and laundry room with a full bathroom, it can be easily converted into rental unit. EXCELLENT LOCATION. Minutes to Schools, Golf Course, Brentwood Mall, Lougheed Mall, Costco, and Skytrain. (28986759)

PublicRemarks: Located in the heart of Brentwood, Tailor by Marcon is a community tailored to all with only minutes walking distance to Brentwood Skytrain station, Brentwood Mall, Whole Foods, Starbucks, major banks, Winners, and only a few minutes' drive from Costco, BCIT, SFU, CEFA, Deer Lake Park and much more. This stunning corner 3-bedroom sub penthouse features an airy 10'6" ceiling, high efficiency heating and air conditioning system, expansive windows, 30" Bosch appliance package, full height pantry, floating vanity motion sensor lighting in ensuite, 2 EV-Ready parking stalls and l locker included. Premium amenities including a fully equipped fitness Centre, yoga/stretch room, co-working area, dog run and much more. (29188202)

PublicRemarks: Think Whistler, but in New Westminster! Custom built in 2011 5 bedroom, 5 bathroom log executive home, including a legal 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom basement suite. Vaulted entry way, huge flex room, river rock fireplace, jetted tub, and stainless steel appliances are just a few of the main home features. Large basement suite (1142 sq ft) is updated with new flooring, baseboard, new bathroom updates, and more. Separate entrance, shared laundry. New hot water tank and high efficiency furnace. Fenced yard, outdoor pool and hot tub are a bonus to this unique and full of character home. Situated in a great neighborhood close to schools, and amenities. (29280661)

PublicRemarks: Amazing opportunity to live in one of Burnaby North's sought after neighbourhoods - Government Road! South facing with an extensive patio and deck area of almost 250 sq ft. overlooking the lovely private, treed rear garden Alert to all artists and handimade - the studio is perfectly located overlooking the garden. The main floor offers both formal dining and and a separate kitchen eating area, with loads of custom made cabinets. The family room is adjacent to the kitchen and main foyer for easy access. The upper level has 3 good size bedrooms with a 3 piece Primary ensuite. Double attached garage with inside entry and loads of extra parking available. Minutes to major shopping malls, Metrotown, Schools and Transit. This home is perfect for the growing family and is ready for a new owner. (29373342)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to one of Burnaby's most desirable neighborhoods, Buckingham Heights! This 3 level warm character home features a spacious layout, large bedrooms, extensive wainscoting, hardwood floors & moldings, 9´ ceilings, sunroom, and large covered front porch. The basement is fully finished and has separate access. The large private backyard offers privacy, a relaxing greenspace, and ideal for gardening, entertaining family, friends, and a safe place for kids to play. Perfect for day-to-day family living and entertaining. Convenient walking distance to Buckingham Elementary, public transit and Deer Lake Park. Don´t miss out, Call today! (29225768)

PublicRemarks: You'll never find this again! Unparalleled luxury in this one-of-a-kind private penthouse. PublicRemarks: Perched high on the hill in one of Van East's premier neighbourhoods sits this spectacular property with ocean, mountain, & city VIEWS. Quiet & peaceful, yet with easy access to Downtown, HWY 1 & North Shore. This bright & airy family home combines a functional 2,445 sqft floorplan on 2 levels. The open living upper level with 2 beds, den, 2 baths, family room, vaulted ceilings, granite counters, 4 burner gas cooktop, air con, & solid 1/2" oak hardwood. The lower level consists of stunning foyer, large laundry room, & massive 2 bedroom garden level suite. Parking for 3 including a 2 car garage with ELEVATOR. A solid home with sprinkler system, copper plumbing, radiant & hot water heat, 2" X 6" perimeter & shiplap construction. OPEN HOUSE SUN FEB 18, 1 - 3 PM. (28954724)

PublicRemarks: Luxury brand new custom built high quality home located in a beautiful tree lined neighbourhood in East Burnaby. This home features an open concept with a modern and functional layout of 7 bedrooms and 6.5 bathrooms. The basement has a two bedroom suite and another one bedroom mortgage helper. The home features a beautiful chefs kitchen, with lots of room for entertaining, ample outdoor living space, air conditioning, 2-5-10 warranty, and all the comforts of a BRAND NEW HOME. Sit on your covered deck and enjoy the views of both mountains and the city scape from the main and upper floors. This is a truly one of a kind opportunity - it will not last long! (29375545)

PublicRemarks: R1 property in Prime Lower Deer lake location, 10 minute walk to Deer Lake. Rare opportunity: build a large, quality home in the most desirable neighborhood in Burnaby. PublicRemarks: Exceptional Home, Immaculate Condition! Open concept main floor has Eclipse door that fully opens to a large covered deck with gas fireplace & gas bbq hookup. Smart home features: control lighting automation, security cameras, house alarm, etc... controlled from your phone! Legal 2 bedroom suite with separate laundry & entrance. Bonus media room with bar & full bathroom or can be used as another bedroom. Nicely landscaped, fully fenced private yard. 2 car detached garage plus prkg for 4 more vehicles. (29310771)

PublicRemarks: Experience the charm of a 1938 Vancouver Heights gem, seamlessly blending historical allure with contemporary sophistication. Step inside to discover refinished hardwood floors guiding you to a large renovated gourmet kitchen, expanded footprint from its original design. This culinary haven showcases a 6-burner Wolf stove, built-in bar fridge, and subtle under-counter lighting, perfect for hosting & culinary delights. Architectural touches, like graceful curved windows, bathe the home in natural light. The renovated bathroom's luxury, with in-floor heating. All complemented by built-in vacuum, hot water on demand & security features. Outdoors, a Southfacing fenced yard boasts a lush perennial garden, a brick pizza oven for alfresco dining. With lane access, envision a future laneway house. (29244872)

PublicRemarks: Nestled in the premier "Queens Park" neighborhood, this beautifully renovated Heritage-style home offers a spacious, family-friendly layout with 4 bedrooms, a flex space, & 2 modern renovated baths upstairs. The main floor with solid hardwood  floor features a traditional living room with a cozy gas fireplace, an elegant dining room, a  powder room, a stylish eat-in kitchen, & a family room that seamlessly opens to a covered patio with a gas fireplace, overlooking the landscaped backyard. Most renovation job was done in 2021 with new appliances,new  cabinets cooktop,reverse water clean system.Air-conditioner in Master bedroom was installed in 2021.More updates...  Epitome of modern luxury. With a double-car garage and a quiet side street location on a 7304 square ft lot.Perfect family home! (28954234)

Property.Address.AddressText: 311 LIVERPOOL STREET|New Westminster, British Columbia V3L1K4

PublicRemarks: This beautiful 3 level house located in South Slope Burnaby with gorgeous mountain and river view. 6 Bedrooms and 7 Bathrooms. Basement can accommodate families with separate entrance and laundry. Huge kitchen for family gatherings. This house has solar powered system, the whole house is fit with German windows. The sewer system is drained by gravidy, no sump pump. The owner spent $100,000 for the exterior stone cladding. Attached Double garage is equipped with electric car charger. Easy access to Richmond and Airport. Close to Metrotown Shopping center and Crystal Mall. School catchment, Nelson Elementary and Burnaby south secondary. Open house: Feb 17/18 Sat/Sun 2t-4PM; Offers will be collected Mon Feb 19 at 2 pm per IDRPO (29335507)

PublicRemarks: ONE OF A KIND! Contemporary residence boasts unobstructed Million $$ Views of City, Mountains, Ocean, Burrard Inlet. This reverse plan home features open concept living at it's finest on upper floor. Expansive Nana Glass Doors open up completely to large deck for indoor & outdoor living with gorgeous backdrop of Sunsets, Cruise Ships, Fireworks, City & Mountains. Access to Roof Deck off this level for panoramic views & entertaining. Main level is comprised of primary suite with Dream en-suite & French doors leading to private deck overlooking sparkling pool. 2 additional bdrms & laundry rm complete this level. Lower level has self-contained living space with kitchen & separate entry. Expansive use of natural stone imported from Brazil & Italy. Addt'l features incl A/C, Radiant Heating, HVAC. (29229487)

PublicRemarks: Luxury and elegance converge with a high walkability location in this timeless residence! This fully renovated home combines an updated Heritage exterior with a modern interior. Enjoy spacious 10ft ceilings on the main floor providing ample room for family activities, entertaining + home office. Enjoy triple paned windows, engineered hardwood floors, Italian-imported kitchen hardware and modern lighting. The spa-like Master bathroom features floor to ceiling tiles, heated floors and  a sinker tub. Exterior upgrades include a new roof, siding and drain tiles. Enjoy every season on the alluring all-cedar deck with spacious backyard. Meticulously landscaped.  The house comes with a modern 2 bdrm basement suite mortgage helper, fully gutted. Turnkey home in the heart of the vibrant Uptown New West! (29135106)

PublicRemarks: Air Conditioning on main and upper floor. The original owner, 9 years custom built house in the Height. Has a beautiful North shore mountain views. The high ended kitchen appliances with double sided fridge and the built in oven, in the middle has a huge granite island. Gas fire place in the family room, by the side it has a 5' x 6' covered - roof Solarium room. Upstairs with 3 large bedrooms and 2 full baths. Primary bedroom has a 3'2 x 5'8 walk-in closet. The basement suited has a separated entrance at the back yard. Double garage on the south facing back yard with lane access. Walking distance to all kinds of shops, element school, the bus transits and community amenities. (28796417)

PublicRemarks: INVESTORS or BUILDERS ALERTS! This large full Duplex comes with four suites, sits on a large corner lot of 9274 sf, R4 Zone with potential to build four units as per latest Burnaby City R4 Zoning, plus potential for higher density as per Burnaby OCP. This great location, two blocks off Hastings, easy walking distance to Kensington Mall and Burnaby North Secondary school, BBY Mountain, Restaurants and cafes. Almost 5000 sf living space with ten bedrooms and five baths, owners occupy two units, long term tenants on the other two units. Parking access can be from Duthie or Union Street. (Buyers should verify all property and zoning information with City of Burnaby). (29111771)

PublicRemarks: The McEvay Blair Multifamily Group of Marcus & Millichap is pleased to present 228 Manitoba, a desirable family-owned apartment building in one of Western Canada's best rental markets. Consisting of 9 bright and spacious suites (6-1 bedrooms and 3-2 bedrooms) that have been renovated with new kitchens and bathrooms, this building boasts a tremendous location right next to Tipperary Park with a 15 minute walk to both Queen's Park and the Columbia Skytrain Station in downtown New Westminster. The property has recently been improved with a new hot water tank, double-glazed windows, and an upgraded lobby and common areas with new carpet, paint, and lighting. There is a substantial amount of storage throughout lending to the potential to add an additional unit for further revenue. There is favourable financing available consisting of an assumable CMHC loan with People's Trust with a current balance of ~$1,226,000, a 10-year term (due 2031), 30 year amortization, and a 2.41% interest rate. (34160347)

PublicRemarks: A brand new STUNNING OFFERING built with luxury and comfort in mind! Grand foyer with vaulted ceilings usher you into your spacious living & dining w/gas fireplace and custom flooring throughout. Step into your Chef's kitchen w/high end appliances w/gorgeous cabinets & backsplash which opens up to the family room w/gorgeous built in TV wall. Guest bedroom w/ensuite round out the main along with a spice kitchen and mud room. Upstairs you'll find 3 large bedrooms w/custom cabinetry & ensuites. This home also features a 2 bedroom legal suite below and a potential in law suite for flexibility as well as a theater room, covered deck with built in bbq, glass railing staircase, radiant floor heat, HRV, A/C  and so much more! Close to many amenities with easy access to highways. A MUST SEE! (29355128)

PublicRemarks: Prime Burnaby location!!! Situated in Upper Deer Lake with a stunning view of the mountains, this property is conveniently close to transit, shopping areas like Metrotown, schools, parks, and recreational facilities. The home boasts a bright and spacious layout flooded with natural light. Notable features include granite kitchen counters, ceramic tiles, laminated hardwood flooring, and Caesar stone vanity counters. The house also includes three fireplaces, a self-contained two-bedroom basement suite, a private fenced backyard, RV parking with lane access, and a two-car garage. With R5 zoning, there is potential for 2 side by side family dwellings. (29179782)

PublicRemarks: North Burnaby´s prime Forest Hills neighbourhood! Featuring a huge 4664 square ft renovated house sitting on a massive 9722 square ft lot with beautiful landscaping through out the property! Renovations include hardwood flooring, vinyl windows, kitchen cabinets/countertops/SS appliances, upgraded 200 amp electrical panel, air conditioning & a gas fireplace with also an original wood burning fireplace! The backyard is very private surrounded by hedges & features an enormous deck which is partially covered with a peaceful zen garden to relax & enjoy. Double car garage with a 400 square ft storage crawlspace above! Rental suite in the basement which can be used as a 2 or 3 bedroom! Steps to Burnaby Mountain Golf Course! Minutes to SFU, Lougheed Hwy & skytrain. OPEN HOUSE Sat Feb 17, 3-5pm & Sun Feb 18, 2-4pm. (29369476)

PublicRemarks: This well maintained high-quality home located in Burnaby most desirable deer lake area, build on over 9000sqft lot, minute away from Deer Lake. This house has over 200K renovation, include new roof, siding, windows, garage door, front door and so much more.  Functional floor plan offers 4 large size bedrooms, spacious living and dining rm, open concept kitchen with maple cabinet, breakfast nook with skylights. Beautiful mini Buchart garden style Front and backyard,  Gorgeous flower beds all over, get away shed, park like setting with benches, many artistic features throughout the garden. Buckingham elementary and Burnaby central secondary catchment. Call today book your private showing!  Open house SAT & SUN (Feb 17,18) 2-4 pm. (29360886)

PublicRemarks: VIEW VIEW VIEW!!! Semi-water front stunning unblocked water view property from all 3 levels. Prestigious quality built home located in desirable North Burnaby area on a cul-de-sac street. Gorgeous street appeal in this beautiful south facing home with million dollar views from all 3 levels. Luxurious touches inside including custom gourmet kitchen with butlers passage leading to stunning dining area featuring fir wainscoting ceiling. Viking appliances, marble counter top, fir wood doors and moldings, hardwood flooring on all 3 levels, heat recovery ventilation and radiant heated floors. Walk out basement to landscaped flat backyard including a second glass fenced deck area and patio. Very close to SFU, and transit. Elementary: Westridge Elementary, Secondary: Burnaby North Secondary (29096944)

PublicRemarks: This beautiful brand new house offers everything you desire. The open concept floor plan creates a spacious & inviting atmosphere, with a living room, dining room, kitchen, spice kitchen, & den on the main floor. Upstairs, you'll find 4 bedrooms & 3 baths, perfect for accommodating your family's needs. The legal suite, additional room, & large rec room with bar in the basement provide ample space for extended family and extra income. Enjoy modern high-end finishes, built in appliances, radiant floor heating, security system with CCTV, & AC for ultimate comfort. PublicRemarks: Welcome to Upper Deer Lake! This beautiful 4 bedroom & Den, 3 bathroom fully renovated single-family home offers partial mountain views. The backyard is fenced in for privacy and the location is central, with close proximity to shopping, schools, and more. The basement is fully finished and includes a kitchen and separate entry. PublicRemarks: Nestled in popular South Slope in Burnaby, this exceptional SOUTH FACING custom-built home offers a spacious layout for a large or extended family with city views extending to the Fraser River. The main floor presents a welcoming living room, family room, dining room, well-appointed kitchen with S/S appliances (2022) & adjacent eating area. A main floor bedroom, a den (or 2nd bdrm) & full bath provide easy access for elderly parents. Upstairs, discover four generously sized bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms & an open study area. The lower level features a two bedroom suite w/separate entrance, ideal for guests or income potential. The back yard leads to a lane w/future potential. Close to 2 elem schools & Bby South H/S, near Metrotown & Marine Crossing shopping. (29298835)

PublicRemarks: This brand-new residence, featuring 8 bedrooms and 6 baths, is tailor-made for hosting and entertaining. Bay windows flood the ground floor with natural light, creating a bright and welcoming atmosphere. The kitchen is a chef's delight with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a wok kitchen. Radiant heating and laminated flooring add to the allure. Ideally located in South Burnaby, this home strikes a perfect balance between convenience and spacious living, offering a refined and contemporary lifestyle. (29304706)

PublicRemarks: This gorgeously built 2 story house is well designed, with a nice layout and clear distinction of functionality: the three bedrooms and 3 bathrooms on the 2nd floor, among which the ensuite bathroom of the master bedroom is equipped with a jet bathtub. The large center island at the living room is perfect for entertaining. The high ceilings designed at the first-floor entrance is magnificent!The 2 independent suits at the first floor are great mortgage helpers. PublicRemarks: Exclusive custom built Noort Home on a corner lot in a quiet cul-de-sac. Main floor features wire-brushed oak floors, 12' high ceiling w/multiple skylights to create a sun-filled great room. The gourmet kitchen boasts Kitchen Aid Pro Series appliances, Brazilian granite counter-tops, island cooktop, extensive cabinetry and walk-in pantry. The open floor plan combined with a private walk-out patio, yard and garden, providing the ideal space for entertaining. 4 large bedrooms and 3 baths comprise the upstairs. The master suite boasts a massive walk-in closet and 5-piece bath with a standalone shower and soaker tub. 2 bedroom suite with a separate entrance, offering plenty of private space for extended family or renting. Full Air Conditioning & Smart Home System. Open House Feb 17 3-5PM (29334707)

PublicRemarks: Ideal for investors (5.0% CAP Rate), or owner operators alike. Royal LePage Westside Klein Group Commercial presents #100 ' 624 Agnes Street, 4 ground floor Retail Strata Units, part of a 4 Storey Mixed-Use strata building located in downtown New Westminster. This high traffic retail property is ideally located on Agnes Street and is only minutes away from the BC Land Title Office, the Provincial Court of BC, and both the Columbia Skytrain station and New Westminster Skytrain Station. This location offers convenient access to all regional amenities as well as to both HWY1 and downtown Vancouver. This property features 3,967 SF of ground floor retail space, extraordinary wide street frontage, an open lay out, high ceiling heights, interior office and storage, private washrooms, kitchenette, five (5) exclusively designated underground parking stalls, four (4) additional paid dedicated rental underground parking stalls with lots of customer street parking and loading. (33456195)

PublicRemarks: Absolutely stunning residence nestled in one of South Burnaby's sought-after METROTOWN communities. This remarkable home come with 7 bedrooms and 7 bathrooms. Upon entry, the grand foyer with soaring ceilings welcomes you into the formal living and dining areas. The chef's kitchen and separate wok kitchen feature stainless steel appliances, perfect for culinary enthusiasts. Adjacent to the kitchen, the family room showcases custom cabinetry and opens onto a spacious covered deck, ideal for outdoor entertaining. Upstairs, discover four bedrooms and three baths, including a luxurious master suite with a stunning ensuite and balcony offering picturesque southern views. The basement level includes legally permitted suite, perfect for providing additional income. (29358902)

PublicRemarks: Custom built Executive Dream home in prime Burnaby location on a MASSIVE 15,000 sq. ft. lot. This high quality European built home is an entertainer's dream. Walking distance to Lakeview Elementary (28874826)

PublicRemarks: Private, quiet 10,802 SF corner property. Located in the prime section of Buckingham Heights, away from busy Burris & Canada Way! Very well maintained, 2nd owner, 3 level West Coast Contemporary home in immaculate condition! Vaulted & Cove ceilings! Arched entry. Open to below Foyer/an attractive, expensive chandelier! 5 bedrooms up are ALL good sizes! 4 bathrooms. Skylight. Kitchen opens to eating area which opens to walk out backyard! Side by side oversized sub Zero fridge. Huge 6 piece ensuite w/jacuzzi tub! Suite potential w/sink/kitchen cupboards & exterior door from basement. 3 fireplaces w/floor to ceiling stone/brick. Hardwood floors. Crown mouldings. Newer blinds. 2 rec rooms +ample storage! 3 car garage w/high ceilings for overhead storage! 2018 ext. paint. (29370704)

PublicRemarks: Discover a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to own an extraordinary lakefront property in Burnaby, where the value lies primarily in its expansive land. This remarkable piece of real estate is one of only eight, and it presents the perfect chance to create your dream home in a highly sought-after location across from the pristine Deer Lake.Situated amidst the tranquil beauty of Deer Lake, this property offers a serene escape from the bustling city while being conveniently close to all urban amenities. The land itself holds immense potential for development, allowing you to envision and construct a residence that perfectly suits your vision and lifestyle. Collecting rent while waiting for your dream home to be built. Contact us today to explore the possibilities! (29236516)

PublicRemarks: Experience Luxury in this brand new 3-Level Home. All the Modern Features offered today. Hot Water Radiant Heat on the main and upper floor, hot water baseboard heating for the basement. R/I Air Condition. Auxiliary Studio with 2 piece bath, electric baseboard heating, perfect for a home studio. Engineered Wood Floors on Main and Upper Hallway. Upper Bedrooms are laminated. Basement with Vinyl plank. 539 Sq ft Legal Suite plus a Separate Suite for a Nanny's quarter or extended family. Fenced Back Yard. Exterior Hardie Board, Stone, Luxe Board. Attached Garage with hot water baseboard heat, 3 Open Parking spaces and room for a Motorhome. Central Location to Rec Centres, Scotia Barn, Burnaby Hockey Winter Club, Christine Sinclair Centre, Shadbolt Centre for the Arts, Deer Lake Park and Burnaby Lake, Metrotown and Amazing Brentwood Shopping. Close to Burnaby Central Secondary and BCIT and Simon Fraser University. Easy access to Hwy. 2-5-10 Year Home Warranty. (29364373)

PublicRemarks: Discover an exceptional family home in a prestigious government road area, boasting a spacious layout and an unfinished basement for personalized customization. Nestled in a neat and friendly neighbourhood, this residence is close to the highly-ranked Seaforth Elementary School. Situated on a 17,185 sqft. lot, the property features a front yard, a huge private backyard, and a top floor with three bedrooms, two bathrooms. The main floor offers plenty of spacious area for rec room, dining room, a living room and more. Plus, enjoy a jetted hot tub inside the main bathroom for relaxation looking out the nature. The lower floor, with a separate entrance, provides flexibility for a nanny suite or versatile entertainment space. (29333679)

PublicRemarks: New Modern luxurious house. Open floorplan on main with 10 ft. ceiling. Good size office/bedroom and full bathroom on the main floor. Upstairs features 3 good size ensuite bedrooms, master bedroom with bathtub, plus separate shower. Close to Safeway, Brentwood Town Centre, Skytrain, Shops and restaurants. WELCOME OFFERS! (28980830)

PublicRemarks: Rare opportunity! Welcome to this 3-level spacious custom built house in the central location Burnaby South Slope with fantastic views, Right south facing on a high-end corner lot. Radiant heating throughout on all levels, A/C on main and upstairs, HRV & security system. 5 bedrooms on the main & upper level. Basement includes two separate entrance one-bedroom suites with laundry, great mortgage helpers. Double garage plus nearly 8 additional parking stalls. 7 Bed, 6 bath, 4 kitchens. Fully fenced private gated yard & covered sundeck. Great location & community! Just one minute walk to Clinton Elementary, steps from transit and Burnaby South Secondary, minutes to Metrotown, T&T, Royal Oak Skytrain Station, restaurants, services & more. Motivated for sale, book your viewing today. (29208700)

PublicRemarks: Builders Alert! Great investment opportunity in Burnaby North. A fantastic opportunity to own this 8,778 sqft (66x133), R12 zoned subdividable lot to build front/back duplexes potentially. This two level home has 3 bedrooms on the main level. A huge recreation room, kitchen, bedroom and separated entrance on below level. A short drive to Metrotown, Brentwood Mall, Holdom Skytrain station, Burnaby Hospital, BCIT & easy access to Hwy 1. School Catchments: Douglas Road Elementary & Burnaby Central Secondary. French: Inman Elementary, Cascade Heights Elementary, Marlborough Elementary & Moscrop Secondary. (28964911)

PublicRemarks: Great opportunity to call this central property yours. Ideal for moving in or investment. PublicRemarks: Beautiful BRAND NEW home on a large 10,244 sf lot in most desirable South Slope area. This stunning home has a fantastic floor plan and offers incredible Richmond city views. The main floor offers high ceiling and bright natural light brought in by large windows. Open concept main floor includes a spacious beautiful Kitchen, spice kitchen with granite countertops, nook, Office, living/dining area, Balcony, and spacious entry. Top floor has 4 BDRMS with own private baths and balcony views. House is equipped with Central AC, Security system and surround sound speakers. The Basement has a two bedroom legal suite as well as a bonus potential for another suite. (29180849)

PublicRemarks: Discover your dream home nestled in the heart of Burnaby, boasting an expansive 4,510 sqft of elegant living space. This stunning property features 6 generously sized bedrooms and 6 beautifully appointed bathrooms, ensuring comfort and privacy for all members of the family. Gourmet Kitchen: A chef´s delight, equipped with top-of-the-line appliances, perfect for hosting and everyday family meals. Double Garage: Ample space for cars and storage. Metrotown, Crystal Mall, and Brentwood. Easy Hwy #1 access. Ideal for families seeking comfort and convenience in a prime location. Don´t miss this opportunity! (29243565)

PublicRemarks: The Akimbo PENTHOUSE by Imani Development - an architectural masterpiece proudly designed by award-winning IBI Group Architects. This north facing PENTHOUSE features 2,050 square feet of living space & 900 sq.ft Patio. Akimbo offers generous, luxurious sense of space with over-height ceilings, floor-to-ceiling windows, state-of-the-art kitchen, spa-like bathrooms, individually controlled air conditioning & heating for year-round climate control throughout the home. Centrally located in Brentwood, conveniently close to shopping mall, restaurants, groceries, transit & highways. GST is not included in the purchase price. 2 parking stall & 1 locker included. Showing by appointment only (29258760)

This home offers Miele Appliances With amazing layout designed by an experienced expert, includes spacious Living & Great room, fancy kitchen paired with a large natural stone counter island, condo full size wok kitchen, 3 ovens, commercial level gas stove etc. Upper level has 4 good size rooms with en-suite or J&G. PublicRemarks: A spectacular custom built 3 levels home located in sought after Vancouver Heights. Sophisticated open floor plan with grand impressive high ceiling foyer & tempered glass railings. Also features European cabinets, waterfall counters, central air conditioning. Upstairs offer 4 large size bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. Master bedroom has a spa ensuite and balcony. Main floor has mid living room. Dining room a dream gourmet kitchen & a wok kitchen. Spacious family living room and a bedroom with full bath. Basement has 2 separate entrances with 1 bedroom-kitchen unit and a 2 bedroom-kitchen unit. Walking distance to Confederation Park, Eilieen Daily Community Centre, Burnaby Heights shops, restaurants, bus transit, Rosser Elementary & Alpha Secondary schools. (29340448)

PublicRemarks: Stunning Euro-style new house by CitiDesign in desirable Sullivan Heights area, 9125 sqft corner lot near City of Lougheed & North Road Village. 5793 sf floor area, double volume entry lobby, cozy gas f/p, gourmet kitchen with Quartz countertops, S/S appliances, high ceiling, Great Room, glass doors to the roofed deck & den w/ensuite. Upstairs has 4 bedrooms, each w/ensuite, incl. a south-facing Master BR w/soaker tub, shower, & double sinks. Basement has a 2BR legal suite, home theatre, guest bedrooms, and more living spaces. Heat-pump heating & Eco-Air A/C for year-round comfort. Potential Laneway Home up to 1507 sf. Easy walk to parks, Cameron library/community centre, schools & Lougheed Mall. (28228276)

PublicRemarks: This GORGEOUS home located in on of the best street in the neighborhood. it offers supreme finishing give a feeling of warm & modern luxurious. Open functional floorplan with 10 ft. ceiling height on main. Spacious high ceiling foyer with large storage closet. Oak engineer hardwood flooring through main and upstairs. Open gourmet kitchen with luxury built-in F&P appliances, large waterfall island, extensive use of luxury quartz countertops and backsplash. Functional wet bar by the dinning area. Huge south facing cover sundeck. Two bedroom legal suite in the basement, huge recreation room with wet bar, potential for  extra one bedroom suite with separate entrance. Central location! Close to Brentwood Town Centre, Skytrain, Shops and restaurants. (29249581)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to 5380 Gilpin Street, luxury living in the heart of South Burnaby with 7 beds and 6 washrooms! The main floor features a grand foyer as you enter, a dining room, a den, massive great room, kitchen, wok kitchen, nook, and the mud room/laundry room with a separate entrance. Upstairs features the primary bedroom with a walk in closet and its own ensuite plus 3 more bedrooms and 2 washrooms. Downstairs features a rec room, a bedroom with a WIC, full washroom and a 2 bedroom legal suite. In addition, this home features AC, Control 4 automation, radiant heated floors, HRV, stucco, lawn sprinklers, back lane access, and CCTV cameras. Centrally located with Metropolis at Metrotown, schools, and major routes minutes away! (29374262)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to the modern masterpiece, where unobstructed, breathtaking panoramic VIEWS of Water, PortmanBridge & Mountains will greet you. Open concept floor plan with natural light through Euro-line windows, complemented by European glass stairs, hardwood floors, and custom light fixtures. Gourmet chef's kitchen is a culinary haven, equipped with high-end stainless-steel appliances, exquisite cabinetry & custom finishes. Built-in features like TV, speakers, security cameras & 2 zone heating & cooling systems with Icomfort Ultra Smart thermostats. 7 bdrms, 7 baths & 4,300 sqft of space, this contemporary home caters to the entire family. Nestled in Burnaby's sought-after neighborhood, THE CREST, and offering a sizable two-bedroom legal suite as a mortgage helper, it epitomizes modern luxury. (29361447)

PublicRemarks: Burnaby Lake location! 41 X 207 Lot with backlane. Beautifully Modern built home over 5000 sqft. TOTAL of 10 BDRMS, 10 BATHS, 3 KITCHENS. Top floor has 4 BDRMS, all BDRMS are spacious & come with private BATHS. Laundry is located upstairs. Master BDRM located on the Northwest side with views of Vancouver. OPEN CONCEPT main floor is entertainers paradise with full master room & high ceilings. Modern high end designer kitchen, Fisher Paykel appliances. Oversized Island with seating & beautiful hanging lighting. Extra big size WOK kitchen. Eclipse doors combining indoor family room to outdoor covered patio. 10ft ceiling on main, Control 4 Automation, A/C, designer fixtures, hardwood floors & more. 2 BDRM Legal suite + Media & 1 BDRM suite. Steps to Canada Way, parks, Schools, Shopping & bus. (29110256)

PublicRemarks: Presenting a Burnaby North gem-a stunning, one-of-a-kind residence on an 8,873 sq.ft lot with captivating views and nestled on a greenbelt. PublicRemarks: Fantastic European design rarely found in the Sperling-Duthie! 17' high foyer, finest solid wood curved stairway leads you to upstairs 4 spacious bedrooms, each one with magnificent South city/North Mountain view. 12' high living room to impress your honor guests. Family gathering in the 9' high family room equipped with a great size open kitchen and handy enclosed wok kitchen, huge bay windows, entertain downstairs in a TV Games, Home Theatre... Walking distance to Burnaby North Secondary, close to SFU, shopping and golf course. Since zoning is R4 and land 8K sqft, there is a good chance to build a laneway home at North West corner with city's permission. (28918902)

PublicRemarks: Brand New Luxury three-story Mansion in Central Burnaby. This gorgeous home boasts an open concept with 9 bedrooms, 9 FULL bathrooms and a 2-bed legal suite with separate laundry. PublicRemarks: Welcome to 4069 Clinton Street! Custom built owner occupied! PublicRemarks: Jewel of Capital Hill, built by Supna Homes! Nested on the westside of the hill. Boasting 6 BDRMS & 7 BATHS, this stunning residence spans over 3400 sq/ft across 3 lvls, offering an abundance of space and comfort. Enjoy extraordinary 270-degree views encompassing Burnaby, Richmond, Vancouver downtown, ski hills, & the iconic Lions Gate Bridge from three decks, including a private rooftop oasis. The high-end finishes throughout showcase the home's exquisite craftsmanship, while the integration of smart home technology, Control 4 automation, and state-of-the-art systems for lighting, music, and blinds add a touch of modern convenience. A legal two-bedroom basement suite, providing both functionality & additional living space. Situated just minutes away from the Capital Hill viewpoint! (29364442)
