PublicRemarks: Enjoy the south slope sunshine new house. Customized and built in extra care. Large kitchen with many sunlight and nice view. Extra sound reduction material applied inside the bed room walls, including basement walls. New house warranty is in place. 2 bed room legal suite of mortgage helper with walk out entrance. Private back yard with lean access. Opportunity to build lane way house over 1000 sf with power and water supply line prepared. Burnaby South Secondary school, golf course, shopping, restaurants, parks nearby. Several minutes walk to bus station, easily transfer to sky train. Open house 2-4 pm, January 27, 2024 (Saturday) (29272333)

PublicRemarks: Experience the luxury of this beautifully designed and impeccably built custom home! Featuring 9 beds & 10 baths, modern designed interior with functional layout, 2 balconies, private backyard, and an outdoor patio. The Stunning kitchen features high end JennAir appliances, gorgeous granite counters/backsplash, and modern sleek cabinets. Appointed with the features you and your family deserve, this home includes 4 luxury primary bedrooms w/ensuite spa-like bathrooms, amazing wine glass wall, expansive bar, and a rough-in theatre room with separate entrance downstairs. Roughed-in utilities in accessory building to convert into additional rental suite. Up to 3 potential mortgage helpers! This home is not to be missed! (29245823)

PublicRemarks: Quality new home great layout done with attention to detail. Prime North Burnaby, quiet street, level lot, sunny yard. Schools Aubrey and Burnaby North. Very bright home. Welcoming entry, living room is on the left, den with walk-in closet and full bath on the right. Dining room has French doors to a deck. Open style kitchen with massive island that opens to a family room with extra high ceiling that flows out to a huge covered south exposed deck. There is a 2 piece guest washroom, spice kitchen and a mud room. 4 bedrooms up all with ensuite baths and fully organized closets. Basement has a legal two bedroom suite & flex space for nanny quarters & a media room. Triple garage plus room for an RV on the side. lots of yard for a garden. A must see. No open house all viewings by appointment (29036972)

PublicRemarks: Professional high quality 7 bedroom + 7 bathroom home located in a quiet neighbourhood. Custom built 3 level house in Parkcrest with a family friendly yard & covered patio for entertaining. Close to Holdom Station, Burnaby North Secondary School, Kensington Plaza, bus transit, and elementary school. SFU is approx. 10 min drive. The Amazing Brentwood Mall is approx. 5 min drive away. High quality stone kitchen island, countertops, exterior and floor tile throughout. 2 car garage parking + 2 car private/gated parking in the back. Wet bar, theatre room, 2 bedroom basement suite and city views. Call today for your private showing! (28143181)

PublicRemarks: [OPEN HOUSE: 2-4 FEB 11] Best custom built mansion in town! Meticulously designed with great attention to details, featuring Brazilian cherry hardwood floorings, Air Conditioning & HRV throughout, serving window connecting Wok to main Kitchen, 4 bedrooms above & 3 en-suite rental bedrooms below, yielding over $3,000/month. Large front & side yards, sunny South facing backyard, EV-ready detached Double Garage, and so much more. Located on a quiet street, this corner lot is measured 59' x 124' with convenient lanes access. Just steps from shopping complexes like Station Square, Metrotown, Crystal, Old Orchard, Central Park, all its amenities such as Chip&Putt, tennis courts, & lots more. Book your private showing today. You will be delighted ! (29015835)

PublicRemarks: Spectacular Mountain, City and Park view. Forest Glen Park slopes down to Deer Lake with the North Shore mountains in the background. This incredible 7-bedroom, 8-bathroom house sits on a 7,420 sqft lot with over 4,500 sqft of living space. It features 5 ensuites and two mortgage-helper suites with separate entries. High-quality build with HRV, A/C and built-in vacuum. High-end material and appliances, wok kitchen, extensive use of crown mouldings and many more features. Enjoy a low-maintenance backyard and a stunning city park in front with cherry tree-lined streets and unobstructed North Shore Mountain views. Steps to shopping mall, BCIT, Moscrop High School. (29004672)

PublicRemarks: Upper Deer Lake. BRAND NEW, Custom Built over 4400 square ft of Quality, Luxury. Grand Entrance 20'3 Ceiling in Foyer. Open Living/Dining/ Family/Kitchen (plus large Wok kitchen). Bedroom on MAIN with full ensuite plus walk in closet, 4 bedroom up stairs all with ensuites. High End Stainless Steel appliances,. Legal 1 Bedroom Suite in basement with potential for 2 more suites. Media Room. H/W Radiant Heat. Air Conditioning. Roughed in for EV Charging. 602 square ft Garage with rough-in bathroom plus 2 Car open parking. Walking Distance with trail down Brantford to Deer Lake Park. Minutes to Metrotown Shopping, Crystal Mall, Rec Centre on Kensington overpass including Burnaby Hockey Winter Club. PublicRemarks: Discover this rare gem in Burnaby's Government Road neighborhood-a spacious haven on a 16,000 sq.ft. lot. Hardwood floors and two fireplaces enhance the living space, while large windows fill the rooms with natural light. Four bedrooms, three bathrooms, and a bonus one-bedroom in-law suite offer versatile living options.  The vast lot provides endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment, from a dream garden to potential development. Perfect for various lifestyles, whether you're looking to develop or move in, this property awaits your vision. (29187582)

PublicRemarks: This Stunning Elegant Masterpiece has all the charms in a dream home. Built on three levels, this home is spacious, luminous, and designed with open concept. Extensive use of wainscoting, moulding and indirect lighting. The main floor, with high ceilings, art-gallery walls and chef's gourmet kitchen with highend appliances, massive island, and wok kitchen. 4 generous bedrooms up with spectacular ensuite. 10 & 9 ft ceiling throughout, HVAC, AC, instant hot water system, video security, radiant heat, fully integrated home audio & sound system. Level 66x144 fully fenced southern exposed yard with inground sprinklers. Outdoor kitchen, large fire pit with granite table top. Tastefully landscaped, like new condition. Golf course, SFU, Brentwood Mall within minutes. Open house Feb 10 & 11 2-4 (29229517)

PublicRemarks: Modern Luxurious Mansion located on a large 8,742 sf corner lot offers over 4,800 sf of gorgeous living space with amazing North Shore Mountain views and a beautiful Brentwood city view. The custom-built home features a fabulous open layout design, high ceilings on all three levels, a huge gourmet kitchen, and a wok kitchen with custom-cut granite countertops, high-end Miele stainless appliances, radiant heat, a smart home system, A/C, HRV, engineered hardwood floors, and much more. Three large bedrooms upstairs are all ensuite, with the master bedroom boasting a huge walk-in closet and balcony. Downstairs includes a theater room, a nice-sized laundry room, a sauna room, and a spacious wine cellar. This property is conveniently located steps away from Metrotown shopping. (28835350)

PublicRemarks: SOUTH FACING, STUNNING WATER, MOUNTAIN AND CITY VIEWS. This beautiful new home is located on a quiet residential street in Vancouver Heights, one of the best locations in Burnaby Heights. Large deck with outdoor fireplace on main. Large balcony from master bedroom and rooftop patio with unobstructed northshore water and mountain view. 3 bdrms on top floor, one ensuite bdrm on main plus one bdrm with bar and game room in the basement. This house also has a two bdrms legal suite in the basement which is a good mortgage helper. Total of 7 bdrms & 7 bathrooms. Super convenient location, quick access to downtown Vancouver, North Vancouver, SFU, shopping and Hwy 1. Elementary: K-7 Gilmore Community, Secondary 8-12 Alpha Secondary. (29190473)

PublicRemarks: Nestled near Marine Way and Boundary Road, this property is the paramount hub for office and light industrial activities in Greater Vancouver. Seamless access to Vancouver, Burnaby, Richmond, Coquitlam, Delta, Surrey, Vancouver Airport, and the US border makes it highly strategic. The nearby Market Crossing Shopping Centre adds practicality. The building boasts versatile office spaces, lab improvements, a showroom, and a warehouse with a 9'6 x 11'6 loading door. Easily divisible into two units, it offers flexibility for varied business needs. Men's and Women's washrooms on both floors, a first-floor showroom with a shower room, and 12 offices on the second floor enhance convenience and functionality. The 6,778 sq. ft. corner office in Marine Way Business Park features abundant natural light, an HVAC system, and four front parking stalls, catering to businesses in search of a central, adaptable, and well-equipped workspace in Greater Vancouver. (34507381)

PublicRemarks: Discover the ultimate lifestyle in North Burnaby. Exceptional architectural design distinguishes the interior and exterior. The open living area includes a formal dining room, an office, and a gourmet kitchen with an additional wok kitchen on the main floor. On the top floor, Each bedroom boasts its own ensuite luxury bathrooms and with elegant drop ceiling details, and plush carpets. The basement features one bedroom, 2 full bathrooms, wet bar, laundry room and media room with Karaoke Jukebox. EV Charger is installed in front of the garage. This smart home is complete with air conditioning, a serene Zen garden, and essential gadgets for modern living. (29037297)

Dont wait long builders, this big change is coming fast! (27630883)

PublicRemarks: Discover Burnaby North's gem at 8260 Manson Drive, located in the highly sought-after Government Rd area. This exceptional Westcoast contemporary home sits on over a 10,000sqft lot bright south-facing rear backyard, offering the perfect blend of natural light from the east and west sides. Ideal for hosting/entertaining and growing your family. Highlights - spacious driveway, 3 car enclosed garages, a custom pergola with a brick firewood-burning oven, hot tub, and a putting green. The spacious upstairs includes 4 bdrms with ensuites, the open main with an office, workshop, and a full ensuite guest bdrm. The basement boasts a spacious 2-bdrm suite, rec/media room, and a nanny quarters. Fine details throughout must see to appreciate. (29330520)

PublicRemarks: 7707-7735 Kingsway , 2 lots for sale, 17,245 sf in total . This location benefits from proximity to an array of amenities close by from residential , retail & Metro town a major shopping centre . Both properties are currently leased for $10396 .22/month until 2025, Seller pays taxes .  Based on the current Edmonds Town Centre Plan,  subject lots are designated as RM2 District and subject to a suitable assembly with max. allowable Floor Area Ratio 1.9. Three lots are owned by the city, they will sell at market value. City of Burnaby is undertaking a review of the Edmonds Town Centre plan now, they do imagine this corridor along Kingsway to allow for more density than the previous  plan (RM2). Possibly 6 storeys with ground-level commercial use (at minimum) will be allowed. The new plan is still in the works and is contingent upon additional public consultation and Council approval. (34343059)

PublicRemarks: Avison Young is excited to present a rare opportunity to acquire a 10,848 sq. ft. strata unit with dock loading in the heart of North Burnaby, near the BCIT campus. This unit provides unparalleled exposure fronting along Wayburne Drive, and direct access to Highway 1 and Willingdon Avenue, providing easy connectivity to all areas of Metro Vancouver. Conveniently situated near the Gilmore Skytrain station and Rupert Skytrain Station, it offers transit connections to Downtown Vancouver, Surrey, and the Tri-Cities. Available for immediate occupancy.   Nearby amenities include Brentwood Town Centre, the Amazing Brentwood Shopping Centre, and Metropolis at Metrotown.  Professionally managed strata.
